reviews.reviewText: I had a good feeling when I first saw this product. The price was great and it looked amazing. It came in a very small lightweight box and it was pretty easy to assemble. The 2nd pic shows that it has (7) shelves that can hold about 4 pairs of sneakers and has a bottom shelf that has drawers to keep stuff in and has side pocket storage!!Definitely recommend this product!!!

reviews.reviewText: I’ve had this shoe organizer for a few months not and unfortunately ima be tossing it. While it is nice and it does hold a hood about it is pretty weak. I know I when over the shoe limit instead of 32 I put 40. I wear size 5 so I figured it wouldn’t be a big deal, But oh it was. I’ve come come to it toppled over and shoes everywhere. I used duck tape to try and hold it together and that did help for to long. The bars are dented in. As well as getting anything other then sneakers, flats, or sandals is hard because the tiers are so close together. I’m giving 3 starts because I put 8 more pairs of shoes that wasn’t recommended so that’s on me. I think this would a good for kids shoes or maybe a male who doesn’t wear anything high top
